      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KISS AND RUN (7) was well fancied last time and led throughout to score (22.76) at this track in a Grade 5 over 400m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Can measure up again. AT THE GATE (1) did a good job to finish third last time out over 350m at Grafton (20.45) in a Grade 5, the second top-three finish on the trot. Key player on best and worth another try. PITMAN GO WELL (4) finished fourth last time but the start prior broke the clock when winning over 388m at Gosford, taking a Grade 5 in a quick 22.30. Smart winner two back and looks a key chance on that form. MR. SPECKLE (2) is right in the mix.",
